## State Management
- Use context-loader for persistent state
- Pass state as explicit parameters between skills
- Log state transitions for debugging

## Integration Notes
- Receives tasks from Claude Code environment
- Returns results to Claude Code for user presentation
- Uses context-loader for shared memory
- Validates with verifier before presenting results
